body_html: The readme for 1.3, https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/r1.3/tensorflow/core/profiler, does not contain a reference to ProfileContext. It appears ProfileContext was added after TensorFlow 1.3, so you have to use the master branch to use it.

body: The readme for 1.3, https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/r1.3/tensorflow/core/profiler, does not contain a reference to `ProfileContext`. It appears `ProfileContext` was added after TensorFlow 1.3, so you have to use the master branch to use it.
